## 🧱 Technical Fixes
- Optimize title and meta description lengths to recommended limits (50-60 chars for title, 120-155 chars for meta).
- Ensure all images have descriptive alt attributes for better accessibility and SEO.
- Implement structured data markup (e.g., product schema) to enhance search result appearance.

## 💡 Conversion Optimization
- Add clear and prominent calls-to-action (CTAs) on product pages and landing pages.
- Simplify navigation and filter options to help users find products faster.
- Use trust signals such as verified reviews, secure payment badges, and easy return policies.

